      "body": "<p><strong>Source queued:</strong> https://study.com/academy/lesson/video/the-texas-revolution-lesson-for-kids.html.</p><p><strong>Source type:</strong> Url. <strong>Class-maker credibility tag:</strong> Secondary.</p><p><strong>Source URL:</strong> <a href=\"https://study.com/academy/lesson/video/the-texas-revolution-lesson-for-kids.html\">https://study.com/academy/lesson/video/the-texas-revolution-lesson-for-kids.html</a></p><p>No extractable text was available for this source.</p><div class=\"source-quality\"><p><strong>Credibility ranking:</strong> Moderate. <strong>Reliability ranking:</strong> Moderate.</p><p><strong>Information-literacy finding:</strong> Readable source text was available during generation. Use it for supported claims, and corroborate statistics, forecasts, or disputed points.</p></div>"
